3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a problem of finding the optimal transformation and considers a possible solution, which is a topic in data structures and algorithms.
4. cs.CG (Computational Geometry) - The paper deals with finding shortest PC cycles and paths in edge-coloured multigraphs, which is a topic in computational geometry.
5. cs.CO (Combinatorics) - The paper discusses results and conjectures related to properly edge-coloured paths and cycles in edge-coloured multigraphs, which is a topic in combinatorics.
